nodes.documentation:
@title BankSetup

* @dev @notice This contract allows :
              1. Central bank to setup, close and reopen settlement banks
              2. Central bank to create and remove settlement banks role
              3. View bank details
              4. Settlement bank to create, close and view moible number account for their clients
              5. Keep transfer fund transaction records between settlement banks

* @author Cheryl Kwong
nodes.name: BankSetup
createBank
reopenBank
removeBank
getBankDetails
addMobileNumber
removeMobileNumber
getMobileNumberBanks
addMobileRecord
getMobileRecord

devdoc.author: Cheryl Kwong
devdoc.details: @notice This contract allows :              1. Central bank to setup, close and reopen settlement banks              2. Central bank to create and remove settlement banks role              3. View bank details              4. Settlement bank to create, close and view moible number account for their clients              5. Keep transfer fund transaction records between settlement banks

addMobileNumber(uint256,address).details: Create mobile number account for client by settlement bank     Only settlement bank can perform this function

params.bank: the settlement bank which holds the mobile number account

addMobileRecord(uint256,address,uint256).details: Keep records of fund transfer between settlement banks for the mobile number account     Only settlement bank can perform this function

createBank(address,string).details: Create a new settlement bank account     Settlement bank role create

params.bankName: the name of the settlement bank

getBankDetails(address).return: bankName : the bank name of the search bankauthorization : indicate if the bank is active or close

getMobileNumberBanks(uint256).details: Retrieve the registered banks of mobile number account     Only settlement bank can perform this function
getMobileNumberBanks(uint256).return: bank list belongs to mobile number

getMobileRecord(uint256).details: Retrieve records of fund transfer between settlement banks for the mobile number account     Only settlement bank can perform this function

isOwner().details: Returns true if the caller is the current owner.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

removeBank(address).details: Remove a settlement bank account     Settlement bank role remove     Only contract Owner can perform this function

removeMobileNumber(uint256,address).details: Delete mobile number account for client by settlement bank     Only settlement bank can perform this function

params.bank: the settlement bank which holds the mobile number account

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

reopenBank(address).details: Reopen an closed settlement bank account     Settlement bank role added     Only contract Owner can perform this function

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
